in august1983 the long awaited big envelope a document for cuhk admission arrived it was in the afternoon and i had not been doing anything when the postman with his big bag knocked on the door i knew what it was about i hurriedly opened the envelope and my mood at that time is hard to describe it lasted several hours and only calmed down later
i received a letter from a distant friend